---
const siteName = "Visio Nova Mundi";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Impact — {siteName}</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <a class="back" href="/">← Back to Home</a>

      <h1>Impact (CIC)</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        We build public-benefit initiatives designed to help people in practical, measurable ways —
        with long-term sustainability at the core.
      </p>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>What we do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Community support and direct help</li>
          <li>Long-term programs with measurable outcomes</li>
          <li>Partnerships, transparency, and accountability</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>How it’s funded</h2>
        <p>
          Visio Nova Mundi develops ventures that generate revenue. Profits are used to support the
          CIC mission and scale impact responsibly.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #0b0f19;
    color: #e6e8ee;
  }
  main {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 20px;
  }
  .back {
    color: #b7bfd6;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .back:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 18px 0 10px;
    font-size: 40px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .lead {
    color: #b7bfd6;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
  .card {
    margin-top: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 18px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }
  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 20px;
  }
  p,
  li {
    color: #b7bfd6;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
